trans-unit.source: Specifies whether a column type is visible in the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView"></xref> designer.

trans-unit.source: By default, types derived from <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewColumn> appear in <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView> control-specific parts of the Visual Studio designer, but inherit a <xref:System.ComponentModel.DesignTimeVisibleAttribute> of <xref:System.ComponentModel.DesignTimeVisibleAttribute.No> to prevent them from appearing in other parts of the designer.
trans-unit.target: Som standard typer som härletts från <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewColumn>visas i <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView>kontroll-specifika delar av Visual Studio-designer ärver men en <xref:System.ComponentModel.DesignTimeVisibleAttribute>av <xref:System.ComponentModel.DesignTimeVisibleAttribute.No>att förhindra att de visas i andra delar av designern.</xref:System.ComponentModel.DesignTimeVisibleAttribute.No> </xref:System.ComponentModel.DesignTimeVisibleAttribute> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewColumn>

trans-unit.source: This is necessary because the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewColumn> type implements the <xref:System.ComponentModel.IComponent> interface, which normally makes an instance of the type appear in the designer.
trans-unit.target: Detta är nödvändigt eftersom den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewColumn>skriver implementerar den <xref:System.ComponentModel.IComponent>-gränssnittet, som normalt är en instans av typen visas i designern.</xref:System.ComponentModel.IComponent> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewColumn>

trans-unit.source: Use this attribute to prevent a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewColumn> type from appearing in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView> control-specific designer.
trans-unit.target: Använd det här attributet för att förhindra att en <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewColumn>typ visas i den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView>kontroll-specifika designer.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewColumn>
